name: New-menu-adder-remover
tagline: Add and Remove files from the New menu
body:
#New menu adder and remover
>
>This is a program that will add and remove files from the Windows New menu.
>
####Installation
Use `git clone https://github.com/karstenes/New-Menu-adder-remover.git` to install
####Usage
>
>To use, run either the add or remove batch files.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
